request.description:
Enterprise login response with grouped permissions and permission hash for cache validation.

**Response Structure:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "user": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "email": "admin@example.com",
      "name": "Admin User",
      "role": {
        "code": "admin",
        "name": "Admin",
        "level": 10,
        "is_admin": true
      },
      "permissions": {
        "version": 1,
        "hash": "a1b2c3",
        "grouped": {
          "user": ["read", "write", "manage"],
          "role": ["read", "manage"]
        },
        "count": 25,
        "is_admin": true
      }
    },
    "token": "jwt_access_token",
    "refresh_token": "jwt_refresh_token",
    "expires_in": 900,
    "refresh_in": 604800,
    "token_type": "Bearer"
  }
}
```

