request.description:
Get dropdown data for leave request form (employees with codes and balances, leave types). Requires `leave.read` permission.

**Use Case:** Populate dropdowns in leave request form and display available balance for each employee.

**Changes (v2.0):**
- Added `employee_code` field to employee objects
- Removed `email` field from employee objects
- Added `remaining_balance` field to each employee object (total_quota - used_leave)

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "employees": [
      {
        "id": "770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440003",
        "name": "John Doe",
        "employee_code": "EMP001",
        "remaining_balance": 7.0
      },
      {
        "id": "770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440004",
        "name": "Jane Smith",
        "employee_code": "EMP002",
        "remaining_balance": 12.0
      }
    ],
    "leave_types": [
      {
        "id": "880e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440004",
        "name": "Annual Leave",
        "code": "AL",
        "max_days": 12
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

**Note:** Each employee includes their `remaining_balance` for easy reference when creating leave requests.

Get form select options for create/update contract forms. Requires `employee_contract.read` permission.

**Use Case:** Populate dropdown/select fields in frontend forms.

**Response Example:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "employees": [
      {
        "id": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
        "employee_code": "EMP001",
        "name": "John Doe"
      },
      {
        "id": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
        "employee_code": "EMP002",
        "name": "Jane Smith"
      }
    ],
    "contract_types": [
      {"value": "PERMANENT", "label": "Permanent"},
      {"value": "CONTRACT", "label": "Contract"},
      {"value": "INTERNSHIP", "label": "Internship"},
      {"value": "PROBATION", "label": "Probation"}
    ],
    "statuses": [
      {"value": "ACTIVE", "label": "Active"},
      {"value": "EXPIRED", "label": "Expired"},
      {"value": "TERMINATED", "label": "Terminated"}
    ]
  },
  "timestamp": "2026-02-06T10:00:00+07:00",
  "request_id": "req_formdata_123"
}
```

**Performance:**
- Returns first 1000 employees (sufficient for most organizations)
- No pagination - single request for all form options
- Cache this response in frontend to reduce API calls

**Integration:**
- Use for Employee select/combobox
- Use for Contract Type radio/select
- Use for Status select (if allowing manual status change)
